---
layout: default
title: Nick Ball
description: Web developer based in San Francisco
path: "/"
---

{% macro JobLink() %}
<a
  target="_blank"
  rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow"
  href="https://www.hellosign.com"
  class="font-medium"
>
  HelloSign
</a>
{% endmacro %}

{% macro Post(item) %}
<li class="mb-4">
  <a class="text-lg md:text-xl" href="{{ item.url }}">
    {{ item.data.title }}
  </a>
  <time value="{{ item.date }}" class="text-sm block">{{ item.date | readableDate }}</time>
</li>
{% endmacro %}

{% macro H2(text) %}
<h2
  class="text-gray-700 mb-2 uppercase text-xs md:text-sm font-semibold tracking-wider"
  >{{ text }}</h2>
{% endmacro %}

<section class="mb-12 -mr-24">
  <p class="text-gray-700 text-xl md:text-3xl leading-relaxed">
    Hi, I&apos;m <strong>Nick Ball</strong>, a web developer focused on
    the front end. I enjoy functional programming, design systems, and
    component-based architecture. I work as a
    <strong>front-end engineer</strong>
    at {{ JobLink() }}.
  </p>
</section>

<section class="mb-16 container">
  {{ H2("Posts") }}
  <ul>
  {%- for item in collections.post | reverse -%}
  {{ Post(item) }}
  {%- endfor -%}
  </ul>
</section>

<section class="container mb-16">
  {{ H2("About Me") }}
  <p class="mb-4">
    I currently work at {{ JobLink() }} as a Frontend Engineer building
    complex user interfaces that make it easier for users to work with PDF
    documents and web forms. I work heavily with technologies like
    <strong>React</strong>, <strong>GraphQL</strong>,
    <strong>Elixir</strong>, and <strong>Phoenix</strong>.
  </p>
  <p>
    I was previously at
    <a
      href="https://loudr.fm/"
      target="_blank"
      rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow"
      class="font-medium"
    >
      Loudr
    </a>
    (Acquired by Spotify). I have a B.S. in Management Science from UC San
    Diego.
  </p>
</section>
